INTRODUCTION

Bellabeat is a high-tech manufacturer of health-focused products for women. It is a successful small company, but they have potential to become a larger player in the global smart device market. 

You have been asked to focus on one of Bellabeat products and analyze smart device data to gain insight into how consumers are using their smart devices. The insights you discover will then help guide marketing strategy for the company

You will present your analysis to the Bellabeat executive team along with high-level recommendations for Bellabeat’s marketing strategy.

THE TEAM

Urška Sršen → co-founder and CCO
Sando Mur → co-founder and member of the executive team
Marketing analytics team 

THE PRODUCTS

Bellabeat app 
Leaf → Bellabeat’s classic wellness tracker
Time → wellness watch
Spring → smart water bottle
Bellabeat membership

QUESTIONS

The CCO asks you to analyse smart device usage data in order to gain insight into how consumers use non-Bellabeat smart devices. She wants you to select on Bellabeat product to apply these insights to in your presentations.
What are some trend in smart device usage?
How could these trends apply to Bellabeat customers?
How could these trends help influence Bellabeat marketing strategy?

DELIVERABLES

Summary of the business task
Description of all the data sources used
Documentation of any clear manipulation of the data
Summary of the analysis
Supporting visualizations and key findings
High-level content recommendations based on the analysis 
